away Resort (Maldives) I was very happy to have HIM as Chef. He is a high caliber! He is a very creative, innovative Chef, always up dated and always willing to go the extra mile to satisfy clients' special desires. He was working always under budget, he is a good trainer and team player willing to give his experience to his staff. He created extra staff trainings. He has good eyes to present buffets especially in details. He is fair, strict, honest has a good sense of humor and has always good words for his staff. I can recommend Mr. Möller without any doubts for any exclusive restaurant, 5* resort hotel around the globe and I would re-employ him immediately. I wish him all the best for his further career.", "recommendations/1/name": "Ingo Möller", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Director of Culinary & Michelin Star Pastry Chef || 31 Years in Fine Dining & Banquet Catering || Expert in Bakery, Pastry, Chocolate & Sugar Work || Innovative World Cuisine Specialist || Strong Leadership Skills", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ingo-möller-b469484/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADZ7GYB9BNQvkIC1lifq3NE4R2ujkah6gc", "totalExperienceYears": "18.9", "totalRecommendationsGiven": "2", "totalRecommendationsReceived": "0", "urn": "ACoAAACKUIEBlBwPz24ZbiVm8X8LDKMwDIYwoyk"}$$::jsonb),
